Description:
For Immediate Private Sale, Inspect By Private Appointment
If you're starting out, slowing down or looking for an investment property then look no further. From the moment you walk in the door you will get that warm inviting feeling. Impeccably maintained, exuding classic charm and character, this home offers 3 generous sized bedrooms with built robes, master with walk in robe and ensuite, formal lounge room, spacious kitchen with large meals area and stainless steel appliances. Features include: solar panels, gas heating, air conditioning, spacious courtyard with outdoor pergola and a single garage. All within walking distance to Albanvale primary school and right around the corner from parklands, Brimbank Shopping Centre and public transport. With a home and location like this, why would you want to miss out? Hurry, be the first to step into this lovely home

Description:
Quality Family Living in Incredible Location!
Positioned in a beautiful and quiet court location is where you will find this immaculate property that is sure to impress the fussiest of buyers! Within walking distance to all the local amenities such as Watergardens Shopping Centre and Taylors Lakes Primary & Secondary School, you are also only 5 minutes away from the Calder Freeway. This is truly a special location!
Property Features:
* 4 spacious bedrooms (Master with full ensuite and walk in robe)
* Open Study / 5th bedroom
* Multiple living rooms including a spacious lounge on entry and rumpus room
* Large, qulaity timber kitchen with adjoining meals area
* Central family bathroom
* Roller Shutters
* Large outdoor entertaining space
* Remote Garage
* Ducted Heating
* Split System Cooling
* Gas Log Fire Place
* Solar Panels
* All set on approximately 662m2 of prime Taylors Lakes land!
With an incredible location, large block size and a quality home with scope for further enhancement, sleep on this opportunity and you will miss out. Taylors Lakes is a sleeping giant!
Put simply: This is a very rare opportunity. Call Bassam Salem today!

Description:
Lovely Street Facing Villa with NO Body Corporate!
In a price range that is becoming increasingly harder to find, this spacious villa unit is ideally positioned in the heart of Airport West within walking distance to McNamara Avenue shops, schools, bus service, and within very easy access to Westfield, Essendon Fields and Keilor Road.
Street-facing, on its own title and with no body corporate, this lovely single level home is saturated by natural light, and consists of a spacious lounge, modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, meals area, two large bedrooms with mirrored BIR's, bright central bathroom and a separate laundry. Features ducted heating, split system cooling, alarm system, CCTV, recently replaced carpet, additional parking space in front of the remote garage, and a lovely grassed rear yard & entertaining area.
This lovely villa makes the perfect first home, downsizing opportunity or investment property. Move straight in, or lease straight out be quick!

Description:
FAMILY LIVING - INSIDE AND OUT!
With its updated interior and sensational outdoor entertaining area, this home offers a ready-to-enjoy lifestyle in an ever-popular Keilor East neighbourhood. Beyond its rendered facade, the home's spacious floorplan comprises four bedrooms (master with WIR and modern ensuite), superb main bathroom, big open-plan living/dining area complemented by a stunning kitchen complete with quality cooking appliances and double dishwasher. Other stand-out features include a modern laundry and additional powder room (third toilet), heating and cooling throughout, keyless entry, stone benchtops and vanities, polished hardwood floors. Bi-folds open out to a full-width undercover deck and expansive backyard with decked entertaining area/BBQ kitchen, studio, plus plenty of front off-street parking. Close to primary and secondary schools, public transport, local parks and pool/leisure centre.

Description:
Resort style Oasis!
This charming home embraces a resort - style setting which will feel like you're on holidays 365 days a year. With a great floor plan, immaculate presentation and a striking in-ground pool, this outstanding home offers the ultimate in single level family living.
Showcasing a warm and welcoming living room flowing through to a versatile space perfect as an open study, second dining or play area. The well-equipped kitchen features stainless steel appliances and opens up to a great sized meal area perfect for everyday family living.
A beautiful master bedroom offers a W.I.R and the bonus of semi ensuite access. 2 further bedrooms sit at the rear of the home as well as a beautiful bathroom with double vanity, separate toilet and laundry.
Walk through to the backyard and you'll be amazed by what the home has to offer. An expansive carport with remote roller door access and undercover pergola area offers the perfect space for year-round entertaining. The large salt - chlorinated inground concrete pool is a wow factor and feels completely private to the outside world. Landscaped gardens, a generous sized steel garage and sauna all add to the appeal of this enticing home!
Set on 690sqm (Approx.) and situated in a convenient location just a stones throw away from all the amenities you could desire makes this opportunity one not to be missed!
Extra features include; coonara fire place, split system heating/cooling, carport, solar panels, sauna, dishwasher, electric gate and much more

Close to popular primary and secondary schools, public transport options, Keilor Road cafes, restaurants and renowned shopping precincts.

Description:
Under Offer
Set on a large corner allotment (approx 737sqm), this single-level showpiece presents a family environment without compare thanks to its expansive floorplan, premium features throughout and fabulous indoor/outdoor entertaining spaces. Fully optioned and flawlessly presented, the home's light-filled interior showcases an extra-large master bedroom with WIR and spa ensuite, three additional bedrooms (all with BIRs) and main family bathroom. Along with a dedicated study/home office, the home also includes a formal lounge and expansive open-plan living/dining area enhanced by a well-appointed kitchen complete with walk-in pantry and quality appliances. Ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, ducted vacuum, alarm system and CCTV all add to the appeal, as well as double-glazed windows, solid hardwood floors, efficient LED downlights and high ceilings throughout. Step outside to discover an enormous yet wonderfully private al-fresco entertaining area including two water features, large north-facing backyard with lush lawn area and established gardens, plus four watertanks, handy storage shed, triple garage and additional gated off-street parking (via Winkler Drive). Walking distance to Taylors Creek trails, Keilor Lodge Reserve and popular sports facilities, Robertson Road buses and Overnewton College, as well as easy access to Watergardens Shopping Centre, Watergardens Station and the Calder Freeway. Family perfection!

Description:
A LIGHT-FILLED HAVEN OF EASY-LIVING EXCELLENCE!
On its own separately-titled allotment with no shared land, this immaculately-presented 3BR home offers an outstanding low-maintenance lifestyle opportunity with its surprisingly spacious design, quality features and enviably accessible location. Bathed in natural light, the home's impeccable interior comprises a large master bedroom with WIR and private ensuite, two additional bedrooms (both with BIRs) and modern main bathroom complete with floor-to-ceiling tiles. Adding to its appeal is a separate lounge leading through to the open dining/living area and spotless kitchen with dishwasher, new oven and new gas cooktop. Along with ducted heating and evaporative cooling, the home also includes new carpets throughout and a full-size laundry, plus an undercover patio/entertaining area and substantial backyard, internally-accessed garage (r/c) and additional driveway parking space. Wonderfully convenient yet blissfully quiet, it's close to local buses and Keilor Road trams, renowned eateries and vibrant shopping precinct, primary and secondary schools, Steele Creek trails and parkland as well as easy freeway access.
